A dynamic stadium arena at night rendered in vibrant comic book style with bold ink outlines and halftone dot shading, featuring multiple runners on parallel tracks racing toward a finish line, each lane glowing with different neon colors—electric blue, bright orange, vivid green. The runners are stylized as determined athletes in mid-sprint, their motion captured with dramatic speed lines radiating behind them. Above the stadium, fireworks burst in explosive starbursts against a deep purple sky. The scene conveys intense competition and celebration, with dramatic shadows and high contrast typical of classic comic book illustration. Empty grandstands filled with silhouetted cheering crowds, spotlights cutting through the air creating dramatic beams of light across the track.
